            <div>
              <ul>
                <li>Orthodox Canon.org (beta v1.2) 3/31/24</li>
                <li>You can now close your tab, and have the book where you left off loaded back.</li>
                <br>

                <li>Orthodox Canon.org (beta v1.11) 3/23/24</li>
                <li>This website will go on hiatus for a while, stay tuned!</li>
                <br>

                <li>Orthodox Canon.org (beta v1.1) 3/2/24</li>
                <li>+ New translation (2012 Brenton Septuigant and Byzantine text for New Testament.)</li>
                <li class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-500">+ Red Lettering added.</li>
                <li>+ Improvements to hover highlights.</li>
                <br>

                <li>Orthodox Canon.org (beta v1.0) 2/3/2024</li>
                <li>+ Added a toggle to dark mode.</li>
                <li>+ Added a small highlight when hovering over the verses.</li>


              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
